name: Queen Grace Collection Clair Dress
description:
From the Queen Grace Designer Signature Collection. Fall limited edition series. Introducing the Queen Grace Signature Collection. The Claire Dress. Growl. Could there be a more powerful, sexy feline style animal pattern as the brown leopard print? QQ has selected the boldest, more flattering fabric, cut the sleeves with a ragline shoulder to compliment your beautiful arms, tri-sleeve, black satin high waist panels and perfectly stretchy, body hugging style to accentuate your every move. Knee length hem, open v-neckline.
Claire is also available in our Grey Leopard and Tiger print options. 
Fabric; 95% jersey, 5% poly, 5% spandex. Lining; 100% polyester.

name: Queen Grace Collection Elise Dress
description:
From the Queen Grace Designer Signature Collection. Fall & Holiday limited edition series. The Elise dress is the beautifully shaped, delicately body hugging answer to every curvy girls "little black" dress - complimenting your every graceful move. Contemporary wrap style completes the shape, with an A-line creating a playful silhouette, graceful lace panel back and sleeves with sexy, plunging neckline. Adjustable belt gives you perfect flexibility for the boardroom or night out at party or a club.

Fabric | Outer Shell; 95% poly, 5% spandex
Lace | 100% rayon
Lining | 100% poly
